===Noun===
'''愛護''' ([[あいご]], ''aigo'')

# protection, kind treatment

===Verb===
'''愛護する''' ([[あいご]]する, ''aigo suru'')

# to be kind to

====Conjugation====
{{ja-suru|愛護|あいご|aigo}}

===Idioms===
*[[動物]][[愛護]]の[[精神]] (どうぶつあいごのせいしん, ''dōbutsu aigo no seishin'') - kindness to animals

===Related Terms===
*[[動物愛護協会]] (どうぶつあいごきょうかい, ''dōbutsu aigo kyoukai'') - Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Animals (SPCA)
*[[動物愛護法]] (どうぶつあいごほう, ''dōbutsu aigo hō'') - animal protection law

